        $blog = new \App\Blog([
          'title' => 'The Role of Color in Your Interior',
          'category' => 'Interior',
          'image' => 'http://res.cloudinary.com/https-www-niagaart-com/image/upload/q_40/v1503361572/konten-1-foto-4_jrmqyj.jpg',
          'content' => '<p>Talking about interior and the design, the role of color can&rsquo;t be parted of. Color has an important role and should be given a special attention in the selection process. Choosing color to be applied in interior design as important as choosing the material itself. Basically, every color represents different impression, nuance and also different feeling in interior design.</p><p>Color in interior design represents some meanings which can influencing the room vibes itself, also the color domination in a room can show what image that the owner wants to show. It means, choosing color for interior is not that trivial as it looks, it&rsquo;s because color is really related with psychological-side influences.</p><p>If we classified the color generally, those below are the list of color characters and their influence to your interior design application:</p><p><em>Glaring/contrast colors </em>(red, bright orange, bright yellow, purple, dark blue, black, etc.), those are kind of colors that easily attract everyone&rsquo;s attention. In a positive way, this kind of colors can give some positive energies to the people.</p><p><a href="http://res.cloudinary.com/https-www-niagaart-com/image/upload/v1503361572/konten-1-foto-1_hfg4xi.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://res.cloudinary.com/https-www-niagaart-com/image/upload/v1503361572/konten-1-foto-1_hfg4xi.jpg" style="height:331px; width:500px"/></a></p><blockquote><p><em>Source: http://cdn.decoist.com</em></p><p>Glaring color in the artwork will make a room dominated by neutal color more living.</p></blockquote><p><em><strong>Do: </strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Glaring/contrast color is suitable to be displayed as accent in a room, this kind of color isn&rsquo;t good for dominating room. For example, this color is suitable for a set of sofa in room with minimalist design. If the sofa has that kind of color, other furnitures must in a neutral or low contrast color dominated.</p></li><li><p>This kind of color more suitable in restaurant/caf&eacute; interior, the glaring color can giving a plus value when it comes to selling. It&rsquo;s because this kind of color will attract the consumer attention easily and good for increasing appetite.</p></li><li><p>Giving a little touch of glaring color is never hurt to your living room! It definitely makes the living room more living and warm.</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>Don&rsquo;t: </strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Too much use the glaring colors to furniture, it gives the room less elegant and looks smaller.</p></li><li><p>This kind of color can&rsquo;t be dominating in a room with recess function, such as bedroom interior, especially kids&rsquo; bedroom interior. It&rsquo;s because this kind of color has a bad effect for relaxation.</p></li></ul><p><em>Pastel color</em> (pink, cream<em>, </em>violet, broken-white, pale blue, pale green, etc.), this kind of color quite has a feminine touch. The low contrast character makes this type of color give a soft vibe in your interior.</p><p><img alt="" src="http://res.cloudinary.com/https-www-niagaart-com/image/upload/v1503361572/konten-1-foto-2_rpnycx.jpg" style="height:596px; width:500px"/></p><blockquote><p><em>Source: http://homemydesign.com</em></p><p>Bedroom with pastel colored interior for living a calmness atmosphere.</p></blockquote><p><em><strong>Do:</strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Pastel color is suitable for dominating bedroom interior, it&rsquo;s because this color give a calmness touch to relax and good for increasing sleep quality.</p></li><li><p>Use this kind of color must be balanced with utilizing the others contrast color furniture, this useful for avoiding a monotonous and dull vibes.</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>Don&rsquo;t:</strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Use too much furniture with this kind of color in a dense activity room, it&rsquo;s because furniture with this color will easily look dirt.</p></li><li><p>Make this kind of color dominating your work/office room, because this type of color will give less productive effects, at least you can combine the pastel color with others furniture with bright color, it will be beyond okay. Great and balance composition always lead to great vibes in your room.</p></li></ul><p><em>Fresh Color </em>(bright green, bright blue, lemonade-yellow, etc.), use this type of color in your interior gives a playful and cheerful vibes in your room. People who likes this type of color wants to show a room with more &lsquo;living vibes&rsquo;. Psychology studies say that a bright color can give relaxing effects and stimulating ideas.</p><p><img alt="" src="http://res.cloudinary.com/https-www-niagaart-com/image/upload/v1503361572/konten-1-foto-3_dg23tx.jpg" style="height:389px; width:550px"/></p><blockquote><p><em>Source: https://elsegundocoop.com</em></p><p>Bright color is really suitable for kid&rsquo;s bedroom interior, this color really could bright-up the mood.</p></blockquote><p><em><strong>Do:</strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Give a little touch of fresh color to your work area for living an energetic effect.</p></li><li><p>It&rsquo;s great for played with this kind of color in kid&rsquo;s bedroom interior.</p></li><li><p>It&rsquo;s also suitable for your kitchen interior, this kind of color give a fresh and clean vibes.</p></li><li><p>This kind of color really goes well with a small room, it&rsquo;s because this kind of color giving an impression of a look wider room.</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>Don&rsquo;t:</strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Actually, we can say that this type of color never goes wrong&hellip; when this type of color dominating your room, it is just okay. Your room will be bright and simply beauty. But still&hellip; balancing with other colors is needed. Mix the bright color with others type of color will definitely make your room one step to coziest place.</p></li></ul><p><em>Neutral color</em> (black, white, gray)<em> </em>is a tricky color to be used in furniture. But, if the composition is suitable to each other, the neutral color in interior will give a simplicity and futuristic vibes in your room. Minimalist design basically use this type of color as the main color, because this type of color is the most effective one to designate the simplicity yet elegant design.</p><p><img alt="" src="http://res.cloudinary.com/https-www-niagaart-com/image/upload/v1503361572/konten-1-foto-4_jrmqyj.jpg" style="height:322px; width:500px"/></p><blockquote><p><em>Source: renopedia.sg</em></p><p>Neutral colored interior will get along well with glaring color</p><p>decorations, like some pillows in the picture.</p></blockquote><p><em><strong>Do:</strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Except black, neutral color is a really good choice to be chosen as the dominant interior color for any room functions.</p></li></ul><p>To be noted: you must balancing the neutral color with some decorations, such as frame, vas, artworks, etc. for diminishing monotonous atmosphere.</p><ul><li><p>You can choose black color only for accent in the room, but if you really want a black furniture fill your space, you can still using it for only one kind of furniture in every room. Just choose one furniture in black in every room, for more dynamic vibes.</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>Don&rsquo;t:</strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Let the room with neutral color felt &lsquo;empty&rsquo; without using some decorations, this kind of situation will make a monotonous vibes. But to make the room with neutral color feels alive, you must using some decorations for diminishing the monotonous vibes.</p></li><li><p>Too much use glaring color decorations which definitely different from the interior dominant color, this thing will certainly make the room less simplicity.</p></li></ul><p><em>Wood color </em>(brown variant color)<em> </em>is a type of color that give a warm and also a friendly feeling whenever it applied in the interior. Using this kind of color will give a balancing vibes between nature and modern-style.</p><p><img alt="" src="http://res.cloudinary.com/https-www-niagaart-com/image/upload/v1503361572/konten-1-foto-5_bzu5fi.jpg" style="height:341px; width:520px"/></p><blockquote><p><em>Source: http://gacahome.com</em></p><p><em>Use plant as a decoration in a room with wood colored domination.</em></p></blockquote><p><em><strong>Do: </strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Wood color usually applied in home located in the mountain territory, or in a place with low temperature. Not only home, but this kind of color is very suitable in villa interior. Because this kind of color is very strong to give warm ambiance.</p></li><li><p>This wood color is great to be combined with the neutral color interior, this combination will definitely give a great ambiance to create a coziness place.</p></li><li><p>Wood color is best to be balanced with the existence of decorations with neutral and bright color.</p></li><li><p>It&rsquo;s great for using plant decorations in a room with wood color domination.</p></li><li><p>Minimalist decorations is the most suitable for a room with wood color interior.</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>Don&rsquo;t:</strong></em></p><ul><li><p>A room with wood color dominated does not really suitable for using the contrast color decorations.</p></li><li><p>Using many decorations, it&rsquo;s because the room with wood color fits with minimalist concept.</p></li></ul><p><em>Metallic color</em> (gold, copper and silver) is the rarest color to be chosen in interior design, it&rsquo;s because this kind of color has a &lsquo;heavy&rsquo; and &lsquo;rigid&rsquo; vibes. But if we can using it properly in the interior, this kind of color can giving an attractive yet futuristic ambiance for a room. Especially for a room with <em>idustrial design</em>.</p><p><em><img alt="" src="http://res.cloudinary.com/https-www-niagaart-com/image/upload/v1503361572/konten-1-foto-6_frn1mi.jpg" style="height:531px; width:433px"/></em></p><blockquote><p><em>Source: http://weburbanist.com</em></p><p><em>Indystrial type which dominated by metallic color is really suitable </em></p><p><em>to combined with wood interior.</em></p></blockquote><p><em><strong>Do:</strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Use metallic color for give a futuristic vibes in room.</p></li><li><p>Metallic color is best to be combined with the contrast color for diminishing monotonous vibes.</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>Don&rsquo;t:</strong></em></p><ul><li><p>Let this type of color stand independently, because it will make a rigid vibe for a room. It&rsquo;s best to use it together with combining metallic color with bright or neutral color furniture.</p></li></ul><p>The role of color is beyond important to create some vibes in your room. So, choose only color that represents your unique personality and the image that we want to tell through the color of interior. For the best result, the key is&hellip; <em>don&rsquo;t be too excessive in applying or choosing the color for every interior</em>, <em>keep it balance to make the color of the room can definitely give the positive effects for the people who have activity within. Because, every color always has a positive side that interesting to be explored!</em></p>',
          'author' => 'Admin',
          'comment' => 'yes',
          'lang' => 'en',
